Compared to the capital, there are a lot of rustic dishes here. Well,
the taste isn't bad though.

Even so, what's up with naked women wandering around? Such a vulgar
bar...

By the way, why are they wearing swimsuits? Is that the trend in this
rural area? ... Hmmm.

In the capital, there's a popular drink called Ice Ale, which is made
using magic to create ice and served ice-cold.

The alcohol here isn't bad either, but once you've tasted that
refreshing sensation, it's hard to go back to something lukewarm...

……By the way, are you inviting me? Sorry, I have a friend so maybe
another time.

I came all the way from the capital to see the ancient city, but there
are really few Rista churches in this town. Did they lose their faith
in God along with the capital relocation?

Well, I guess I was able to see other good things. ...No, it's
nothing.
